Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer.\NYou haven't been bathing lately, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When you moved next to my desk,\Nyou promised
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'd wash every other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit nagging, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a visitor in the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get the visitor a drink yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A visitor at this time of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't been showering either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He smells almost as bad as you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose fault is it that I haven't\Nbeen able to shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This hopeless newspaper can still survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's all because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She's completely oblivious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.56,0:00:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. My name is Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. He really is filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you're a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really tell, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The next target of the middle-aged couple\Nserial killer in Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is in Heidelberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The couple has an adopted daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and that daughter will be taken away\Nby the murderer when she turns 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the adoptive parents will be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you don't know the identities\Nof the couple or the daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That story is so bogus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.03,0:01:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not funny! Please trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a third-rate tabloid\Nwouldn't publish this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not here to sell you a story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,After the twins escaped from the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a blank period of six months\Nbefore the brother was seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My theory is that after they escaped\Nfrom the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,both of the twins came to Heidelberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's your theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then both twins were raised\Nby the sister's current adoptive parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But the brother soon ran away from there,\Nleaving his sister behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You should write a novel,\Nbut I don't think it will sell anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the couple reported\Nthe missing child to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be a news article about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me check your news archive\Nfrom nine years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to stop him,\Nso there won't be any more victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Our boss is allergic to technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the compact editions\Nand original archives from nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And here are the articles that\Ndidn't make it to print.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is the Japanese bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to waste on nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're done looking, just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.\NI guess these crazies show up sometimes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You look good! I'm glad to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so shocked when you\Njust fainted so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you really didn't like\Nthe guy we introduced you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. I just felt ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked to that guy Otto,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and we realized that he's not\Nyour Prince Charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he never
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote you that kind of message\Nin his emails to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that you fainted\Nright after you saw that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me what that man looked like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only a moment,\Nso I didn't get a clear look…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you feel when you saw him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow very familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But not really.\NI don't know how to put this…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Nina. Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to describe it…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same feeling as in my nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea of "absolute evil"\Ntakes us in a theological direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really go to church.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I see that man again,\NI might know the answer clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you could even regain\Nthe lost memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one way to go about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I don't think it's necessary\Nfor you to make it a priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also important for you\Nto think about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do some sports\Nand relieve some stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your worries will go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer, did you stay overnight again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you who let that man\Nuse the archive room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"That man"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I asked him when I saw him earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:07:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that you let him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is still here?\NI can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's about time…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good, isn't it?\NI always eat breakfast here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you go home?\NWhat about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no family since my wife left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I only focused on work,\Nand before I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,my wife had taken my daughter with her\Nto her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to bring them back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I?\NThey were the ones who left me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to go to bring them back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No… You just seemed like you\Nregretted focusing on work so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For men, work always comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If the wife doesn't get it,\Nthen good riddance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It's none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Can I say one more thing, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You smoke too much.\NI'm telling you this as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because she cared about your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Nina's birthday present?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I just finished knitting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Her sweater used to be this small.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to tell her?\NThat she's not our real daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. We don't have to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina is our daughter, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about my future…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Dr. Geitel is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:11:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's meet at Heidelberg Castle,\Ntomorrow night at seven."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow night… Heidelberg Castle…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I am doing this with you\Nwhen I'm so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm facing this mountain\Nof scrap news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it time to give up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, doctor.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If… I'm saying "if"…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go to ask my wife to come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think she'd actually come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she will if you quit smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah!\N-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"An 11-Year-Old Boy Missing."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"While kidnapping is possible,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"so far, there has been no contact\Nfor any ransom demand."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"16 Necker Street." 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a missing person report\Nfrom the Fortners!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's about that news,\Nwe might have something here…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that the killer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,would come for her on her 20th birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If the boy in this article is the brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,look at this.\NHis date of birth is written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the twins' birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dad? I just finished at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to meet up with my friends\Nand go home later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, at Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:13:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But your mother is preparing\Nfor your birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She's meeting her friends\Nbefore coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of friend, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's old enough now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I might finally learn…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,about my lost memories…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If the twin sister is with the Fortners,\Nwhat are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, the family is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call for backup from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The police won't do squat\Nbased on your theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has happened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late if something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will happen!\NIt's all in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me out, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I covered one of the four couple murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The story of the Cologne murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a strange incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell what the purpose\Nof the murder was, no greed or hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like it was only\Nto end people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were there, you would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You say the culprit was a boy\Neven younger than 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think a young man like that\Ncan murder without any emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No kid can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't figure out that murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to say,\Na cliché is all I could come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the work of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If the murderer shows up in front\Nof me now, I will definitely kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 16, Necker Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Sorry to bother you at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Maurer,\Nand I'm from the Heidelberg Post.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you, a news reporter, here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have a few questions…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is it?\N-Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,About the missing person report you filed\Nfor the young boy in 1986…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to talk about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we just ask you a few things?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:16:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a daughter? Is she the twin\Nof the boy who went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is not good.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They prepared a birthday cake for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine years ago,\Nyou fostered a pair of twins. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the girl still with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been caring for Nina
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,as our real daughter all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't make any trouble for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave us be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine years ago,\Nyou took in a pair of twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy has surgical scars on his head,\Nand the girl lost her memory…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner!\NWe have to notify the police right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The lives of you two\Nand your daughter are all in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us see your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she's meeting friends\Nat Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me borrow your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wa… Wait! After we call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to explain\Neverything to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll call the police from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful. Like I said earlier,\Nthis guy is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die on me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back alive. Then I'll quit smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do as the quack doctor said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife will be happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:18:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now.\NHow should I explain this to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my daughter going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Can I borrow your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down… Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone line has been cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, please be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The meeting time has passed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that was just a prank after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to wait… here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asked by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me to get you to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you have to wait here.\NDon't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me so!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna! No, Nina Fortner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me? I'm Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna… Dr. Tenma…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. We'll go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you… my Prince Charming?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to stay and wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He said no one would be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick. Give me something to tie him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When did he say he would be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He just said that he would do something\Nimportant first before coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No… Could it be your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go back to your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later! We have to go, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I can't get it loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:22:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.74,0:22:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, my name is not Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when you were brought to my hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you were Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.29,0:22:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by:\NSandy Huang
